{"tid":1632760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20191007 交通資訊","createTime":"2019-10-06T21:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T22:52:17.000Z","uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8d48c2cef158ed721f69e8a22a023dc313a91d23","tid":1632760,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:37:05.000Z","msg":"(05:07) #港鐵 現已回復有限度服務，服務現況整合如下：<br />\n<br />\n請注意列車服務亦會提早於 晚上6時 結束<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: blue;\">港島綫</span><br />\n每 8 分鐘一班<br />\n西營盤、上環、金鐘、灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后及炮台山站關閉<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">南港島綫</span><br />\n每 8 分鐘一班<br />\n列車服務只來往海怡半島至海洋公園站<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣綫</span><br />\n全綫停駛<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: green;\">觀塘綫</span><br />\n每 8 分鐘一班<br />\n黃埔、何文田、油麻地、旺角、太子、樂富、黃大仙、九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘及調景嶺站關閉<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: purple;\">將軍澳綫</span><br />\n每 8 分鐘一班<br />\n列車服務只來往北角站至油塘站<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: violet;\">西鐵綫</span><br />\n每 8 分鐘一班<br />\n尖東、荃灣西、元朗、天水圍及屯門站關閉<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: teal;\">東鐵綫</span><br />\n每 8 分鐘一班<br />\n大圍、沙田、大埔墟、粉嶺及上水站關閉<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: brown;\">馬鞍山綫</span><br />\n全綫停駛<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: orange;\">東涌綫 </span><br />\n每 8 分鐘一班<br />\n列車服務只來往香港站至青衣站<br />\n<br />\n#<span style=\"color: pink;\">迪士尼綫</span><br />\n全綫停駛<br />\n <br />\n#<span style=\"color: teal;\">機場快綫</span><br />\n下午一點起列車服務只來往香港站及機場站；<br />\n博覽館站全日關閉；<br />\n九龍站市區預辦登機服務全日暫停<br />\n<br />\n輕鐵路綫614, 615, 705, 706, 751及761P暫停。<br />\n輕鐵路綫505, 507, 610, 614P及615P將維持15-16分鐘一班。"},{"pid":"cae3ffafba90624c077ac12f07f6e85f33ef970b","tid":1632760,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />執柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"b345fa9c15a92788032e77ed4770c5005b9ba309","tid":1632760,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:42:41.000Z","msg":"星期二都係咁至好啊，咪又黎全線回復正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78921b2e784a88b2fb12924eec1a5de2d92bd29","tid":1632760,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:46:01.000Z","msg":"完全唔明點解馬鐵要停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d708efa7606ba59f8f271e7bc616870a499495a","tid":1632760,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c78921b2e784a88b2fb12924eec1a5de2d92bd29","tid":1632760,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:46:01.000Z","msg":"完全唔明點解馬鐵要停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:48:12.000Z","msg":"馬鐵拆得勁唔勁？"},{"pid":"3c1a22a64ede59f6f4508710d6c8636f85a94d17","tid":1632760,"uid":164608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:51:41.000Z","msg":"荃灣線全停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb59791ee00c95d4a1ddf4fe933bfaa3a8cf1ac4","tid":1632760,"uid":59289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:27:58.000Z","msg":"新聞稿寫到咁亂，等巴絲出張Empty R 路線圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c373c93d386ec00fd7d67457f0209873c757386","tid":1632760,"uid":37350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:36:56.000Z","msg":"各位要令佢聽日都停<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e72519bbdfbe67ce9f1eeb110bea7235091a9f","tid":1632760,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c78921b2e784a88b2fb12924eec1a5de2d92bd29","tid":1632760,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:46:01.000Z","msg":"完全唔明